# ZMCKit

ZMCKit is a Swift package that provides an easy-to-use interface for integrating Snapchat's Camera Kit into iOS applications. It supports both single lens and multi-lens camera experiences.

## Features

- Single lens camera view
- Multi-lens camera view with carousel
- Custom capture button
- Built-in image preview
- Customizable capture handling
- Simulator support (build-only)
- iOS 13.0+ support

## Requirements

- iOS 13.0+
- Swift 5.9+
- Xcode 15.0+
- Valid Snapchat Camera Kit API Token
- Physical device for running (simulator supported for build only)

